  "update_count": 61,
  "description_snippet": "**VULNERABILITY DETAILS**   \n  \nA FileReader instance is normally referenced in the JavaScript and/or pending_readers_/running_readers_ of FileReader::ThrottlingController in Blink heap. And there is a way to drop all references to FileReader while it's still loading data, which leads to UAF."
